    If [Eiji Nagasumi] is in this Digimon's digivolution cards, increase the number
    of Digimon you can play with this effect by 2.\n[When Attacking] [Once Per Turn]
    By deleting 1 of your opponent's level 3 or lower Digimon, unsuspend this Digimon.
    For each of your Digimon, add 1 to the level this effect may choose.\n[Your Turn]
    Your turn end condition is the opponent having 3 or more memory."
